this a rustic chat using Redis to subscribe / publish messages.

after executing suscriber.js / publisher.js allows you to send a message to the chanel.
here some sample outputs:

-----Redis\redis_cli_chat> node .\publisher.js
send any message to the chat! Hello World!
----Redis\redis_cli_chat> node .\publisher.js
send any message to the chat! This is a sample of a little chat

Subscriber --

-----Redis\redis_cli_chat> node .\suscriber.js
Hello World!
This is a sample of a little chat